This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-vpu layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============
No Deps.

Patches
=======
No Patches

Table of Contents
=================
  I. Adding the meta-vpu layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-vpu layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-vpu'

II. Misc
========
* ./wic -> disk partition settings
* ./recipe-kernel -> kernel stuffs
* ./recipe-devtools/qemu -> machine patches
* ./recipe-core/images -> custom image configurations
